    {
        date: "December 2022 – August 2023",
        title: "Software Technical Support at Campify",
        description: ` • Over 40+ bug fixes were issued.
            • New product module was developed.
            • Usage explanations, and documentation were provided.
            • Quality control was performed on over 20 new features.
            • Optimal user experience was ensured for 50+ customers.
            • Over 150+ complex customer issues were efficiently resolved.
            • Productivity was enhanced by implementing Agile Methodologies.
            
        `,
    },
    {
        date: "July 2021 – February 2022",
        title: "Software Developer at SANNET",
        description: ` • Compliance was given to the SUDEBAN.
            • The application automated processes and filtered information.    
            • Participation was given in a team developing the web application.
            • Responsibilities included development, testing, and participation.
            • Python and Flask Framework were used to implement the application.
        `,
    },
    {
        date: "September 2020 – February 2021",
        title: "Computer Science Teacher at Soroptimist International",
        description: ` • Classes were designed and delivered to women aged 35+ years old.  
